{"tid":1792823,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【和解】關於街頭抗爭一事","createTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-22T18:03:51.000Z","uid":205482,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ecaee1d9e8fbf693eed52a81c7d26f6cc00efa","tid":1792823,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:37.000Z","msg":"利申借ac<br />\n<br />\n最近有唔少人話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">依家無曬街頭抗爭 降曬溫啦<br />\n剩係識和你shop搞經濟同和理非集會</span><br />\n<br />\n咁不如諗下<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">係咪街頭抗爭先最有用？<br />\n是否需要考慮到抗爭損失？<br />\n和理非係咪無用？</span><br />\n<br />\n事實係 <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非集會可以聚集人心 保持熱度<br />\n街頭抗爭的確風險較大<br />\n和你shop初見成效</span><br />\n<br />\n有人認為街頭抗爭有用啲<br />\n咁可以<span style=\"color: violet;\">商量一下有關細節</span><br />\n例如<span style=\"color: violet;\">點樣聚人 邊到聚 之後有咩做</span><br />\n<br />\n但和理非就係和理非 你無可能屌和理非點解唔做勇武<br />\n講好<span style=\"color: violet;\">兄弟爬山 各自努力</span><br />\n和理非有和理非做 勇武有勇武做<br />\n而唔係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武屌和理非無用 和理非屌勇武唔冷靜</span><br />\n否則只會<span style=\"color: red;\">內部分化 運動唔係因為任何一方瓦解 而係因為大家分化彼此而瓦解</span><br />\n和理非同勇武係可以<span style=\"color: gold;\">同時進行架</span><br />\n<br />\nbtw 下晝愛丁堡見 平安夜&amp;聖誕見<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ym6fuTO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fym6fuTO.jpg&h=d44e0385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wD5G9TP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwD5G9TP.jpg&h=3aaf5156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"249acab5758ed65448b3e43b7598a2c9d8cfc1a7","tid":1792823,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a4f0e10af410712bd54723e3f9900c15ef32de","tid":1792823,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T02:53:13.000Z","msg":"大家星期日有時間，記住加入香港金融業職工總會做會員呀！<br />\